Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不必客气 不必手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神器“人格面具”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无不周之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给我和阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他找一个完美无缺的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是抛下男人赴死的女人的最后一个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 维尔赫米纳 塔亚玛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你们一直以来的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们百战百胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“千征令”奥根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 “炎发灼眼的讨伐者”已经缔结了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在她还没熟悉这个世界以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须隐藏她的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 你这种...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手既不是“炎发灼眼” 也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虹 虹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“虹翼”梅利赫姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的决斗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能不先热个身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是热身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 千征令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要验证我的“虹天剑”的威力 你是最佳人选
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 速战速决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你缔结契约时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这契约不是命中注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也会选择这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先从这儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与强者战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身是劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是生死决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是传说中的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也应该有弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会儿就能干掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圈套？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜笠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“炎发灼眼的讨伐者”所披挂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部分羽翼所显现的如意黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以给予强者武器为使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我自愿成为秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有人自愿成为秘器？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为寻找有资格得到我的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自愿成为秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那把大太刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲武士“天目一个”与大太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及制造出它们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个自我混在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出类拔萃的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找有资格得到倾注我生命精华的武器“贽殿遮那”的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为寻找那样一个强者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自愿舍弃了人的一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心无旁骛地以自己的意志 寻找自己的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做你主人的强者就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者啊 接招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳·卡梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了兑现与她的约定才活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都担心会不会马上失去刚刚缔约的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚自己是侥幸获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比训练的厉害一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比“徒”可怕一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然说出了口 就要名副其实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧 包括你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 有人被打倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戈耳迪之结：宝具，形似勋章，实为通信器和自爆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会产生非常剧烈的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢家可以随意处置输家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种条件不应该对女方提出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三项约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吞食人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再骚扰人世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于在我之后出现的“炎发灼眼的讨伐者”...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力地训练她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然打得很艰苦 但我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“虹翼”梅利赫姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就想见你了 炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 维尔赫米纳·卡梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想我们在这里的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达成她的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仅仅只是为此而在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至终都是一个讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成为过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我正看着一个新时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 一个新时代...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“天目一个”的力量只是一把大太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不该发动自在法 与之格斗的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对我们“红世之徒”时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅从外表察知进攻手段是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知外部动作的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部“存在之力”的变化...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得感知到自在法发动的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能松懈对外部的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红世之徒”的自在法能引发不可思议之事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊讶无任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自“红世”者的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话差不多说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}虹天剑：自在法，七色火焰形成剑，通过散布空中的空军（燐子，类似飞在空中的玻璃盾）反射、变化，克敌制胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正看着一个新时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也该分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你长久以来的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和我一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话以前的努力都就白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 无论什么都要独自完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不必担心”就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要照我们所教的做就不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 现在有“天壤劫火”和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我不在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能吃太多的甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我抱抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么喜欢吃甜瓜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在御崎市的调律师 卡穆欣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.66,0:24:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始行动起来的“化装舞会”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.54,0:24:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而暗恋悠二的一名少女知道了真实的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.96,0:24:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的序章
